          "reviewBody": "No facilities are provided, neither the staffs are capable, even labs aren't worth the fees. In such heat waves classes must be air conditioned atleast. Total Waste of Money, better enroll your child in sub urban schools they've far better facilities in this price .",
          "publisher": {
